scene.message:
Nanjo: If only I...{wait_fr:48} if only{nl}
I'd seen her safely home{wait_fr:32}{nl}
back then...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: If we use this power,{nl}
we should be able to pin down{nl}
what caused all this!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Exciting...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Somehow this thrills me!{waitkey}Oh, listen to me{wait_fr:21}{nl}
...do forgive me.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Making fools of us{nl}
like this{wait_fr:48} I won't let it{nl}
slide! I'll put everything{nl}
back the way it was!{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: Damn it, why can't I{nl}
get to the ICU?! There are{nl}
patients there!{wait_fr:21} I have to{nl}
treat young Sonomura...!{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: The TV won't come on,{nl}
and the phones won't connect!{nl}
What in the world is going{nl}
on?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: If only I could find{nl}
the exam room, I could treat{nl}
your injuries...{waitkey}But I don't even know where{nl}
the exam room is anymore!{waitkey}All the rooms have shifted{nl}
around into total chaos!{waitkey}{ret}
